quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  42,1,"Haa, miim."
  42,2,"Ain, siin, qaaf."
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah Te…ó…óu…óo, √Ďee√Īo oon wahayiniri e maa, e …ďeen adinoo…ďe maa."
  42,4,"Ko KaŇčko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuji e ka leydi. Ko KaŇčko kadi woni Toowu…óo, maw…óo oon."
  42,5,"Kammuuji …óiin no e…ď…ďa seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe imsinanoo won…ďe ka leydi …ďeen. Ngandee pellet, ko Allah woni kaforoowo, jurmotoo…óo otoo…óo On."
  42,6,"∆Āeen non jogitii…ďe yi…ó…ďe goo ga Makko, Allah ko deenu…óo …ďe. A wonaani deenoowo …ďe."
  42,7,"Ko wano noon Min wahayniri e maa…óa, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jeertin yim…ďe neene ca'e …óen e won…ďe takko mayre …ďeen, jerrtinaa fii √Īalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'um - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite."
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O wa…óayno …ďe mofte goote. Kono himo oon mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende makko. Too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen non, gi…óo alanaa …ďe, wonaa ballo."
  42,9,"Kaa …ďe njogiti yi…ó…ďe goo ga makko? Awa ko Allah woni Gi…óo on, ko KaŇčko wuurnitata maay…ďe …ďeen; ko KaŇčko kadi woni ka…ótan…óo kala hu'unde."
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondir…óon e fii mun, haray √Īaawoore mum nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko on moo…óon Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]."
  42,11,"Pu…ó…óu…óo kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin. O wa…óiranii on e pittaali mon …óin genndoo…ďe, ka neemoraa…ói kadi nooneeji; Homo …óu…ó…óinira on …óum. Hay hu'unde yerondiraa e makko; ko Kanko woni Nanoowo, ji'oowo On."
  42,12,"Ko KaŇčko heerori soktir…óe kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin. Homo weertana arsike on mo o muuyani, O …ďi…ótinana (mo O muuyani). Pellet, ko O ganndu…óo kala hu'unde."
  42,13,"O sar'inanii on e diina kan, koŇčko ko o yamirnoo nuuhu, e kon ko Min wahayini e maa…óa, e kon ko Min njamirnoo Ibraahiima, e Muusaa e Iisaa, won'de: ""√Ďi…ďnee diina kan; hara on ceertaani e makka"". Kono Ko noddotaa sirkoo…ďe …ďen e mum kon, mawnii e dow ma…ď…ďe. Allah non hino su…ďanoo …óum, mo O muuyani, O fewna e makko, kala tuuboowo."
  42,14,"∆Āe seertaano, si wonaa …ďaawo nde ganndal ngal arde e ma…ď…ďe, sabu bewre hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Si wonaano fii Konngol ardinoongol, immorde ka Joomi maa, haa e lajal ta∆īaangal, √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Ko pellet, roninaaa…ďe deftere nden …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, hino e sikke fii mayre sikkitii…ďe."
  42,15,"Noddu (yim…ďe …ďen) kisan; √Īii…ďiraa no yamira…óaa non, wota a jokku mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe …óeen, maakaa: ""Mi gooŇč…óinii ko Allah jippini kon (fof) e defte, mi njamiraama kadi, nun…óugol hakkunde mon. Allah woni Joomi amen e Joomi mon. Ko minen golle amen woodani, ko onon kadi golle mon woodani. Yeddondiral woo alaa hakkunde amen e mon. Allah moo…ďoyay e denndaandal. Ko ka makko woni ruttorde nden""."
  42,16,"∆Āeen wee√Īiroo…ďe e diina Allah kan, …ďaawo ka ja…ďaneede, hujja ma…ď…ďe on ko mehre, tikkere no fawii e ma…ď…ďe, hino woodani …ďe kadi lepte ca…ótu…óe."
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippiniri deftere nden goonga, e manndakke …óen. E ko anndin maa? Hino gasa hara darnga ngal ko ko …ďadii?"
  42,18,"∆Āeya …ďe gooŇč…óinaani ngal …ďeen, hi…ďe he√Īoringal; gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen kan, ko …ďe hulu fii maggal, e hoore hi…ďe felliti won'de ko ngal goonga. Awa anndee won…ďe yeddondireede …ďen fii Darngal, ko pellet, …ďe ngonii e ndeer majjere wo…ó…óunde."
  42,19,"Allah ko newanii…óo jiyaa…ďe makko …ďen. Homo arsike on mo o muuyani. Ko KaŇčko woni Doolnu…óo, pool…óo On."
  42,20,"Kala taw…óo ko baraaje ndun laakara o faalaa, Men …ďeydanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; kala kadi taw…óo ko jayru ndun aduna o yi…ói, Min ngokkay mo …óum, hara non o alaa ka kaalara (ton) ge…óal."
  42,21,"Kaa hara denndaaaa…ói hino woodani …ďe, sar'inan…ói …ďe e diina kan, ko ko Allah duŇčaaki fii mum? Si wonaano fii Konngol [happunoongol] ngol fii senndugol [hakkunde ma…ď…ďe], √Īaaweteno hakkunde ma…ď…ďe. Ko pellet, hino woodani too√Īu…ďe …ďen, lepte muus…óe."
  42,22,"A yi'at too√Ī…ďe …ďen hino huli e ko …ďe fggitii kon, …óum le ko yantay…óum e ma…ď…ďe. GooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, hi…ďe e dinngire naakooji, hara hino woodani …ďe ka Joomi ma…ď…ďe, kala ko …ďe faaletee. Ko …óuum tigiri, woni …ďural mawnungal ngal."
  42,23,"Ko …óuum woni ko Allah wewlinirta jiyaa…ďe makko gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďen, …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe. Maaku: ""Mi lamndaaki on njo…ďdi e …óum, si wonaa tun giggol en…óam …óam"". Kala paggitii…óo mo∆ī∆īere, Min …ďeydanay mo mo∆ī∆īere e hoore mayre. Pellet, Allah ko kaforoowo, mantoowo."
  42,24,"Kaa …ďe mbi'ay o fefindor nde e hoore Allah fenaande. Si Allah haajuno, O notatno e …ďernda maa nden. Alla no meha meere nden, O tabintinira goonga kan Daalol makko ngol. Pellet, ko O ganndu…óo gunndooji …ďer…óe …óeen."
  42,25,"Ko KaŇčko woni ja…ďanoowo jiyaa…ďe makko …ďeen tuubuubuyee, O yaafoo bon…ói …óin, e hoore Himo anndi ko ngolloton kon."
  42,26,"Himo jaabinana gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen, …ďe ngolli mo∆ī∆īu…ói, O …ďeydana …ďe e …ďural makko ngal. Heefer…ďe …ďen non, hino woodani …ďe lepte ca…ótu…óe."
  42,27,"Si tawno Allah ya√Ī√Īanno jiyaa…ďe Makko …ďeen [fof] arsike, pellet, …ďe bewayno ka leydi; kono Homo jippinira emmbere ko O muuyi. Pellet, ko O kummpitii…óo, yioowo jeyyaa…ďe makko …ďeen."
  42,28,"Ko Kano woni jippinoowo to…ďo ngoon …ďaawo …ďe ta∆īaade, O saaka yurmeende makko nden. Ko KaŇčko kadi woni Gi…óo, jettinii…óo On."
  42,29,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óiin: tagugol kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin, e ruugay…ói …ói O saaki …óin hakkunde majji. KaŇčko e fii moo…ďindiroygol …ďe ngool, si O haajii, ko O kattan…óo."
  42,30,"Kala ko he…ďi on e masiibo, ko sabu ko juu…óe mon …óeen faggitii kon. Himo ya'afoo noon, ko …óuu…ói."
  42,31,"OOn wonaani laawotoo…ďe ka leydi ; alanaa on ga Allah, gi…óo, wanaa ballo."
  42,32,"Hino jiyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óiin: dogay…óe …óen ka maayo, wa'a…óe wa pelle."
  42,33,"Si O haajii, O dee∆īinay henndu ndun, ndu wa…ótinira tabitndu e hoore maggo. Wonii e …óuum, Ma'andeeji, wona 'de kala mu√Ī√Īotoo…óo, jettoowo."
  42,34,"Maa yoolira…óe sabu ko …ďe paggitii kon. Himo ya'afoo noon ko …óuu…ói."
  42,35,"Wennjoo…ďe …ďeeen e aayeeje Amen …óen, hino anndi …ďe alaa laaworde."
  42,36,"Kala ko ngokka…óon e hu'unde, ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; ko ko woni ka Allah koon, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude woni kadi ko heddotoo wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen fawotoo…ďe e Joomi ma…ď…ďe."
  42,37,"wo…ó…óitotoo…ďe bakkaatuuji maw…ói …óiin e paŇčkare …óeen, si wonii …ďe tikkii, hara …ďe yaafoto,"
  42,38,"…ďeen nootii…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe √Īi…ďni juulde nden, …ďe tawata fiyaaku ma…ď…ďe on ko diisondiral hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, nafqoo…ďe e ko ko Min ngarsiki …ďe,"
  42,39,"e …ďeen taw…ďe si bewre he…ďii …ďe, …ďe njottoto."
  42,40,"Njo…ďdi bonnere, ko bone yeru mum. Kala non yaafii…óo o mo∆ī∆īintini, haray njo…ďdi makko ndin ko ka Allah woni. Pellet non, O yi…óaa too√Īoo…ďe …ďeen."
  42,41,"Kala noon yottii…ďe …ďaawo …ďe too√Īeede, ko …ďen woni …ďe laawol [nanngitireede] fawaaki e mum."
  42,42,"Ko laawol [nanngitireede] fawii e mum, ko too√Īoo…ďe yim…ďe …ďeen, hara hi…ďe bewira e leydi ndin ko aldaa e goonga: …ďe …óoon, hino woodani lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  42,43,"Mu√Ī√Īii…óo on kadi o yaafii, ko pellet, …óuum no jiyaa e pellital fiyakuujI."
  42,44,"Kala mo Allah majjini, haray gi…óo (goo) alanaa mo …ďaawo …óum. A tinay too√Ī…ďe …ďeen, tuma …ďe nji'i lepte …óeen, hi…ďe mbi'a: ""Hara laawol ruttorde no woodi?""."
  42,45,"A tinay …ďe kadi, he…ďe mbee…ďitee e magge, hara he…ďe njankinii koyeera on, he…ďe ndaarira ndaar…óe leppagol. GooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen mbi'aya: ""Ko woni hayru …ďe …ďeen, ko …ďen hayrim…ďe ko'e mun e …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin √Ďalnde Darngal"". Nganndee pellet, too√Īu…ďe …ďeen no e lepte duumii…óe."
  42,46,"Yi…ó…ďe alanaa …ďe, ko wallitoo …ďe, hara wonaa Allah. Kala noon mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo."
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado √Īalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa …óuum ka Allah. Nden √Īalnde, faaborde alanaa on, jeddugol kadi alanaa oon."
  42,48,"Si …ďe …óuurnike non, haray min nuliraali ma, aynoowo …ďe: fawaaki ma, si wonaa joottingol. Si wonii Min mee…óiniri ne…ó…óanke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non he…ďi …ďe, sabu kon ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardiniri, a taway pellet, ne…ó…óo on ko jeddu…óo sanne !"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuji …óin e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko o muuyi. Homo ye…óa mo o muuyani …ďi…ď…ďe rew…ďe, O ye…óa kadi mo O muuyani …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe."
  42,50,"maa O jillira …ďe wor…ďe e rew…ďe; Homo wa…óa dimaro, on mo o muuyani. Pellet, ko O gandu…óo, kattan…óo."
  42,51,"Sellantaa ne…ó…óaŇčke, nde Allah yeewtata mo, si wonaa wahayu, maa e …ďaawo heedo, maa o immina Nulaa…óo (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duŇčayee(sakkitoore) makko, ko ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O toowu…óo, √Ďee√Ī…óo."
  42,52,"Ko wano non Min mbayayinir e maa…óa, ruuhu on [Alqur'aana] e yamiroore Amen. A anndaano ko woni deftere, maa gooŇč…óinal; si ko woni, Min mba…óunde ndaygu, ngu Min peewwnirta on mo Min muuyani e jiyaa…ďe Amen …ďen. Pellet, ko a feewnoowo e laawol Pocciingol,"
  42,53,"laawol Allah, On jey…óo ko woni kammuuji e ka leydi. ganndee, ko ka Allah, fiyakuuji …óin nduttotoo."
